Alter capabilities in various ways.

* Blinded
* Charmed
* Deafened
* Exhaustion - see for table
* Frightened
* Grappled
* Incapacitated
* Invisible
* Paralyzed
* Petrified
* Poisoned
* Prone
* Restrained
* Stunned
* Unconscious


