## Alignment ##
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Combination of Morality (Good, Evil, Neutral), and attitudes towards Society and Order (Lawful, Chaotic, or Neutral). E.g. a character or monster can be Lawful Good, Chaotic Evil, etc.

