## Bonds ##
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Connection to people, places, and events in the world. Tie you to things in your background, inspire you to heroism, drive motivations and goals. Whom do you care about? What is most treasured possession? Can gain new bonds over adventures. Create one for your character.

