## Feats ##
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Represents a talent or area of expertise - embodies training, experience, and abilities. Can choose to add a Feat instead of increasing [Ability Scores] when advancing a [Level]. Can gain [Advantage], [Proficiency] in different [Skills], etc. E.g. Alert, Dual Wielder, Healer, Mage Slayer. An optional rule.

